ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="eb8d2e16-376b-4df9-92dc-877581fbca96" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Monthly Feed Usage by Pen Type" CreatedDT="2013-07-18T12:47:23.337" ModifiedDT="2013-10-18T14:18:07.703" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAA0z4=" ReportVersion="1" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select PrimaryPenType, ReportDate, sum(AFQty) as AFQty, sum(AFTons) as AFTons, sum(DMQty) as DMQty, SUM(DMTons) as DMTons, case when sum(AFQty) = 0 then 0 else sum(DMQty) / sum(AFQty) end as DMPct, sum(Cost) as Cost, case when SUM(DMTons)=0 then NULL else SUM(Cost)/SUM(DMTons) end as CostDMTons , InventoryItemName from ( select PrimaryPenType, convert(date, it.TransactionDT) as ReportDate, coalesce(ch.DMPct, it.DMPct) * dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) as DMQty, coalesce(ch.DMPct, it.DMPct) * dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, c.LargeMeasurementType) as DMTons, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) as AFQty, dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, c.LargeMeasurementType) as AFTons, case when iil.TrackingEnabled = 1 and iil.TrackingStartDT <= it.TransactionDT then dbo.GetFifoCost(it.UnitQuantity, it.InventoryItemGID, fsmi.SourceLocationGID, it.TransactionDT) else iil.UnitCost * dbo.GetMeasurementValue(it.UnitQuantity, c.MediumMeasurementType) end as Cost, DropRowNum = row_number() over (partition by it.InventoryTransactionGID order by it.UnitQuantity), ii.InventoryItemName from InventoryTransaction it join Pen p on p.LocationGID = it.ToLocationGID join Location l on l.LocationGID = p.LocationGID cross apply (select top 1 PenTypeName as PrimaryPenType from PenPenType ppt join PenType pt on pt.PenTypeGID = ppt.PenTypeGID where ppt.PenGID = p.PenGID order by ppt.IsPrimary desc) ppt join Company c on c.CompanyGID = l.CompanyGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID join Ingredient i on i.InventoryItemGID = ii.InventoryItemGID join FeedingScheduleDrop fsd on fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID = it.TransactionSourceGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fl on fl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join FeedingScheduleMixInstruction fsmi on fsmi.InventoryItemGID = it.InventoryItemGID and fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fl.FeedingScheduleMixGID join InventoryItemLocation iil on iil.InventoryItemGID = fsmi.InventoryItemGID and iil.LocationGID = fsmi.SourceLocationGID cross apply (select top 1 DMPct from Chemistry where InventoryItemGID = fsmi.InventoryItemGID and LocationGID = fsmi.SourceLocationGID and ChemistryUseType = 2 and AsOfDT <= it.TransactionDT order by AsOfDT desc ) ch ) z where DropRowNum = 1 group by PrimaryPenType, InventoryItemName, ReportDate</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
